WEBVTT


00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:01.820
Never carry in your purse.

00:00:01.880 --> 00:00:03.200
Wanna wear a dress this summer,

00:00:03.201 --> 00:00:05.581
but need a secure place to carry and for your cellphone?

00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:08.880
I wear dresses all summer long, and I actually hate carrying a purse.

00:00:08.881 --> 00:00:11.681
These shorts may hit perfect to have my cellphone on me at all times.

00:00:11.682 --> 00:00:12.561
And when I need to carry,

00:00:12.562 --> 00:00:13.781
I can securely carry.

00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:14.840
Even when I'm sitting down,

00:00:14.841 --> 00:00:16.701
I can still grab things out of my shorts.

00:00:17.120 --> 00:00:18.880
Now I have these shorts to wear under all my dresses.

00:00:18.881 --> 00:00:20.981
I don't have to only wear dresses with pockets.
